overview: Dorian is trying to find his way in the world after suffering an unexpected loss. The Fey visits Dorian one night to offer everything he desires, but what price is Dorian willing to pay for a love he once knew? 'The Fey' is a supernatural horror which demonstrates the way loss and mental health can be entangled, and that sometimes you need help to pull you out of the darkness.
title: The Fey
